{"tid":335991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2010年 高鐵通過的一年 民主黨及公民黨已經盡力了 希望大家不要怪責他們","createTime":"2017-07-26T05:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T09:08:29.000Z","uid":30807,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cdff656aa621220f738ecbe41780a7af12e0097","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100117/13634874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100117%2F13634874&d=mcaRc0iEmC6WJm6dfPyqKozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=18a65f70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100117%2F13634874&h=2c0f32d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100117/13634874</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n難挽敗局泛民無奈棄拉布<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主黨及公民黨反對高鐵撥款申請，但面對保皇派手握立法會過半票數，以及財委會主席不斷限制質詢時間的困局下，兩黨最後放棄拉布戰術，隨即卻遭立法會大樓外反高鐵者批評，要求兩黨拖延會議。有泛民議員坦言已盡力，望反高鐵市民明白，泛民難獨力扭轉敗局。<br />\n據了解，泛民昨晨開會檢討形勢後，認為手頭上的提問越來越少，但政府不斷迴避問題，保皇派又不斷以不同方式阻止他們追問。最重要的是，「唔理我哋幾有道理，保皇派有三十幾票喺手，（撥款申請）一定過到。」<br />\n<br />\n場外人士喝倒采<br />\n有鑑於此，他們決定完成手上問題就不再追問，由社民連接力提出三十多項動議，之後投票表決撥款申請。<br />\n不過，兩黨的決定引起反高鐵人士鼓躁，高呼要求兩黨繼續發問，甚至有人喝倒采。有泛民議員坦言，早知道容許會議結束，必遭場外示威人士批評。「我哋想問問題，政府又唔答，我哋又冇得跟進；保皇派又係咁施壓，我哋冇晒方法。」他希望反高鐵的市民明白，泛民難以獨力扭轉敗局，「<span style=\"color: red;\">一日立法會有功能組別，一日好難扭轉立法會反映唔到民意嘅困局。</span>」"},{"pid":"a5a5b4572246dba9dd26bb41740d44240a687df5","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"同年六月 - <br />\n<br />\n香港政府於2010年推出政改方案，建議2012年立法會選舉的地區直選議席由30席增加至35席，功能界別議席由30席增加至35席，其中區議會界別由現有一席增至六席，由民選區議員互選產生，採用比例代表制。[6]至2010年5月24日，時任中聯辦副主任李剛與民主黨三名核心成員何俊仁、劉慧卿及張文光會面，提出「改良方案」，新增「區議會（第二）功能界別」，由傳統功能組別沒有投票權的市民以一人一票方式選出。<br />\n<br />\n2010年6月中旬，何俊仁以民主黨主席身份建議若政府接受該黨有份參與的「終極普選聯盟」所提的終極普選方案，會建議支持改良方案，更稱不介意民主黨總部被包圍。"},{"pid":"1efb3bf92fa3b4092d2f2aaa3419c0376e656885","tid":335991,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046e862d0c7ad18415b7f44cfb78e576faa99435","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"6月20日，何俊仁出席《城市論壇》時被多名社民連成員和80後包圍。翌日，<span style=\"color: red;\">民主黨在會員大會通過動議，建議贊成修訂後的2012政制方案</span>。這些事件皆引起網民激烈爭議，最後鄭家富、范國威等人因不支持方案而退黨。"},{"pid":"abaf4dd77263a5d2706f7b8dec4fcf6ede058960","tid":335991,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"2010年好精彩"},{"pid":"9344cca7a7f95db4bb4ca18617f36f7ed1d80071","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2010年好精彩</blockquote><br />\n細佬當年仲讀緊i大<br />\n份功課就係拎高鐵做題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243630cd8369a6f3058bf03707c4558b106a8211","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年仲係好支持長毛碌撚大舊"},{"pid":"5899facd249e6461945a3f8812fac0bf571320a1","tid":335991,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同年六月 - <br />\n<br />\n香港政府於2010年推出政改方案，建議2012年立法會選舉的地區直選議席由30席增加至35席，功能界別議席由30席增加至35席，其中區議會界別由現有一席增至六席，由民選區議員互選產生，採用比例代表制。[6]至2010年5月24日，時任中聯辦副主任李剛與民主黨三名核心成員何俊仁、劉慧卿及張文光會面，提出「改良方案」，新增「區議會（第二）功能界別」，由傳統功能組別沒有投票權的市民以一人一票方式選出。<br />\n<br />\n2010年6月中旬，何俊仁以民主黨主席身份建議若政府接受該黨有份參與的「終極普選聯盟」所提的終極普選方案，會建議支持改良方案，更稱不介意民主黨總部被包圍。</blockquote><br />\n個終極普選方案去撚咗邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c59dbfede40dd48d25a8abddbadcd9e5cd30b83","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同年六月 - <br />\n<br />\n香港政府於2010年推出政改方案，建議2012年立法會選舉的地區直選議席由30席增加至35席，功能界別議席由30席增加至35席，其中區議會界別由現有一席增至六席，由民選區議員互選產生，採用比例代表制。[6]至2010年5月24日，時任中聯辦副主任李剛與民主黨三名核心成員何俊仁、劉慧卿及張文光會面，提出「改良方案」，新增「區議會（第二）功能界別」，由傳統功能組別沒有投票權的市民以一人一票方式選出。<br />\n<br />\n2010年6月中旬，何俊仁以民主黨主席身份建議若政府接受該黨有份參與的「終極普選聯盟」所提的終極普選方案，會建議支持改良方案，更稱不介意民主黨總部被包圍。</blockquote><br />\n個終極普選方案去撚咗邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n831<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  民主黨應該樂於接受啦 民主黨一向覺得投反對票都激嬲「呀爺」架啦<br />\n不如接受左再慢慢同佢係細節上討價還價"},{"pid":"62443129d0414b485c263ce9c4da08e502d94572","tid":335991,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e64435f408bd9e08358efe7c6d03959670e63c","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28be27605c444e1f7c10820c88f390dce005db56","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea4574acaabe9d93a7728097f1df63b50823503","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59ab5b1cb5da6c6e6a66073a9496cec7a8b2c1a","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ff20852b737ed5d9a673b717e6805e1dc17253","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c961d5a536cc71fdda4152078bce44ffd997a7e","tid":335991,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4521286c2690e207d7e72a1bef076522be83f2a4","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d737b25dc7a3ad71389ea4d48661d45a4fcc8627","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100117/13634873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100117%2F13634873&d=mcaRc0iEmC6WJm6dfPyqKozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=02cc9e8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100117%2F13634873&h=b1d80a6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100117/13634873</a><br />\n<br />\n身兼民主黨副主席的劉慧卿昨日主持最後一次審議高鐵撥款會議，仍受盡保皇和泛民兩派壓力。當會議開始後一小時，她宣佈將<span style=\"color: red;\">每名議員發問時間，由三分鐘縮至兩分鐘</span>時，即遭包括民主黨在內的泛民成員批評，社民連陳偉業更強烈抗議她有關決定；可是民建聯、工聯會等保皇派議員開腔力挺。"},{"pid":"901c400eea3032d82594c7ce51ff304c63aad7d2","tid":335991,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"無限loop"},{"pid":"5a4e9719b4d158fe957a791e36180f64ade6ae35","tid":335991,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:39:01.000Z","msg":"民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8093878374f67d6156b0b2828c3c0bd63cfbd3d5","tid":335991,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"民主黨賣香港"},{"pid":"e5492283900cf1dd1d586a735487dd24e8b500ba","tid":335991,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83066cb4217bc9d1aac5526048208ec805e8520d","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:48:15.000Z","msg":"唉。。。"},{"pid":"c78a8f7e4272df3ddfb8484e98fdc49368f4694a","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c907af64709ca2476a0dd9f4f83f8baefd1a6e3f","tid":335991,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}